        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em><strong>Consular</strong>:&nbsp;20th level</em><br />Your attunement to the Force is absolute. Your Wisdom or Charisma score increases by 4, and your maximum for this score increases by 4.</p>\n<p>Additionally, you gain mastery over a single force power, and can cast it with little effort. Choose one 3rd-level force power that you know as your signature power. You can cast it once at 3rd level without expending force points. When you do so, you can&rsquo;t do so again until you finish a short or long rest.</p>\n<p>If you want to cast it at a higher level, you must expend force points as normal.</p>",
